_______________________________________________________________________________
"Teleport"         
        This power has 3 uses. First, for a flat 75 sp, the psionicist
        can teleport back to the guild hall. Second, for 10 sp per room,
        the psionicist can set up a movement path of no more than his
        glevel worth in rooms, and will appear at the end of the chain
        without passing through each one. Third, it can be used in
        conjunction with Mental Beacon to teleport back and forth between
        a marked area for a short period of time. You may teleport back
        to your own beacon, or to a shared beacon placed by another
        Psionicist. Can be used to escape, to move about quickly, to
        bypass aggressive monsters, to go somewhere without other players
        knowing where you are going, to aid another Psionicist, etc.

SP Cost:  75 / 10 / 150     Guild Level: 13       Potential Points:  5

Command:  teleport guild, teleport dir,dir,...,dir, teleport beacon,
          or teleport <name> beacon    (To go to <name>s shared beacon)
